## Build & Run

### Prerequisites

- GCC / g++ with C++17 support
- SQLite3 library installed

**Linux / macOS:**
```bash
g++ -std=c++17 -Iinclude src/*.cpp main.cpp -lsqlite3 -o app
./app
```

**Windows (MinGW):**
```bash
g++ -std=c++17 -Iinclude src/*.cpp main.cpp -lsqlite3 -o app.exe
app.exe
```

> If SQLite is bundled as `src3.c`, compile it alongside your source files.

***

